# Master .gitignore for Netspeak Project

# Dependencies
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out

# Environment Variables (CRITICAL)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.production
**/.env.development
**/volumes/db/data/

# OS/IDEs
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.log

# Prisma
**/prisma/migrations/

# Docker
**/volumes/

# Batch Files (Optional, keep them if you want but usually good to ignore local scripts)
# *.bat 
